In [[Islam]], '''Qiyamah''' ({{lang-ar|القيامة|lit=resurrection}}) is the belief in the [[resurrection]] of the people on the [[Day of Judgment]], whether [[Muslim]] or not.<ref>{{Cite Quran|27|36|style=ref}}</ref> In the [[Quran]], ''Al-Qiyamah'' refers to the resurrection.<ref>{{Cite Quran|75|style=ref}}</ref>

According to the belief, ascension to heaven requires belief in the observation{{Clarify|reason=|date=February 2018}} and in the [[Five Pillars of Islam]].<ref>{{Cite Quran|4|48|style=ref}}</ref> It affirms which there will be no [[injustice]]<ref>{{Cite Quran|4|40|style=ref}}</ref> and the [[infidel]] won't be saved.<ref>{{Cite Quran|11|17|style=ref}}</ref>

